modName: FalmerBanes - Ysolda of Whiterun - A Replacer
summary: This is a request for a replacer for Ysolda. She is available nude or clothed in a variant of Farm Outfit 4 . If you choose nude you will have to equip clothing on her via the console. She can be found wandering around Whiterun or if you married her you already know where she is. I also shortened her by about 4 to 6 inches.

author: FalmerBane

files.name: FalmerBanes - Ysolda of Whiterun - Clothed
files.changelogHtml:
Initial Release
I added a version that is a heavier weight at 75 on the slider. You will need to adjust her weight in console and then fast travel or enter exit through a loading door for the change to take effect. This is for people using BBP, UNPB etc.
I added a request for a red head or Auburn version of Ysolda using Apachii Hair. She is under the main files, nude or clothed.
Added two versions of Ysolda with her weight set at 100 in Optional FIles. Please see the screenshot to set her weight in console.
